Package: anya
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fast static malware analysis tool
 Anya performs static analysis on binary files (PE, ELF) to identify
 suspicious characteristics without executing them. Analysis covers
 cryptographic hashes, Shannon entropy, string extraction, PE and ELF
 structure parsing, import table analysis with 40+ suspicious Windows
 API signatures, MITRE ATT&CK technique mapping, and more.
 .
 Results are produced in under a second. No network access required.
 .
 This package installs the command-line interface. A desktop GUI is
 available separately from the project's GitHub releases page.
